    "The difference between the plaus group and the group of all counterfactual explanations is less than 5% for both classifiers.",
    "To first have a grasp of how similar the explanations are between different counterfactual algorithms, we examine the pairwise scaled L0 distances between the counterfactual instances of counterfactual methods.",
